{"tid":1550842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"既然POPO都行緊有罪假定,我地咪用返同一招囉","createTime":"2019-09-07T18:03:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T14:03:05.000Z","uid":5220,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4f5382d7c83710adbe7cce45bd8ea6697a8dea75","tid":1550842,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:03:11.000Z","msg":"要人證明自己係街坊, 證明自己褲袋部手機係自己既<br />\n<br />\n唔該佢地自己證明831冇打死人, 新屋嶺冇強姦囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPOPO一日未證明到自己冇做過, 我地都會繼續講佢地做過呢D野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f884b27c5c2576424828c0a2e7c2edc93d1b1a","tid":1550842,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:03:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0d4253c34fb8779d9c1e09568eb9678146315a1","tid":1550842,"uid":160247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:04:09.000Z","msg":"試下中英都跟住唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》 Glory be to thee, Hong Kong<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流 In angst, tears are shed o&rsquo;er this Land<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨 With rage, fears are crushed, in arms we stand<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透 We rise, undefiled, our voice shall never die<br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡 As we yearn, our freedom nighs<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走 With eyes blinded, long it comes the night<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後 In faith, banners high, we pledge to fight<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透 Our flesh, sacrificed, our blood shall write this song<br />\n建自由 光輝 香港 Free this Land, &ldquo;Stand with Hong Kong!&rdquo;<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜 Stars will fall, and darkness fills the air<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲 Storms will break, bedazzled by our gallant flares!<br />\n捍自由 We shall strike<br />\n來齊集這裡 This perilous night<br />\n來全力抗對 Determined to fight<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅&quot; With hope, with song, with dignity!<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港 Glory enshrined, break our chains! Hold our lines!<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命 Freedom shall rise! Revolution of our Time!<br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽 Liberty thrives, rights divine, in our unending strides<br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港 Glory be to thee, Hong Kong!"},{"pid":"81ac69544d135b461b2ce2ee180476aa3ddda10c","tid":1550842,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:06:43.000Z","msg":"再眾籌登報各國plz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話比其他國家知警察殺人<br />\n被捕人士被失蹤<br />\n<br />\n同埋五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"fd09750e61cf12d17c97e69da3525b40128cc8b5","tid":1550842,"uid":232167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:07:55.000Z","msg":"熱門一個908嘅post都冇？入嚟推兩野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1550800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1550800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0ef7a155d688adfef34d4f64a3e0e76aabbce593","tid":1550842,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:16:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6e808f9fb5f9ba77fe1f3ae68c7d95be1fde9c"